  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.875,
    "endTime": 164.315,
    "text": "Albert, how are you doing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.315,
    "endTime": 165.585,
    "text": "Hey what's up Jun?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.585,
    "endTime": 167.185,
    "text": "What's going on?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.185,
    "endTime": 169.211,
    "text": "Man I'm ready to get my drink on up in here"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.211,
    "endTime": 170.971,
    "text": "for BYB's 30th anniversary."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.826,
    "endTime": 177.396,
    "text": "Now, I asked \"How are you?\" to some of the Japanes people who live in L.A."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.396,
    "endTime": 180.37599999999998,
    "text": "This is how they respond."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.591,
    "endTime": 184.121,
    "text": "Hi Masako-san, how are you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.121,
    "endTime": 185.61100000000002,
    "text": "Hi, how are you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.611,
    "endTime": 186.821,
    "text": "I'm good. How's everything going?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.883,
    "endTime": 189.603,
    "text": "That's good. Nice."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.603,
    "endTime": 190.53300000000002,
    "text": "How (are) you doing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.533,
    "endTime": 191.63299999999998,
    "text": "Good. How (are) you doing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.633,
    "endTime": 193.113,
    "text": "Pretty good man. What are you up to?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.952,
    "endTime": 197.09199999999998,
    "text": "Well um I'm here enjoying myself."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.343,
    "endTime": 199.643,
    "text": "How are you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.643,
    "endTime": 200.993,
    "text": "Hi. Good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.993,
    "endTime": 201.99699999999999,
    "text": "How's everything going?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.997,
    "endTime": 203.51700000000002,
    "text": "Yeah I'm a little tired."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.517,
    "endTime": 204.93699999999998,
    "text": "A little tired today?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.937,
    "endTime": 206.73700000000002,
    "text": "Yeah but it's OK."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.832,
    "endTime": 208.702,
    "text": "HI Koyama-san. How are you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.702,
    "endTime": 209.682,
    "text": "HI. Great."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.682,
    "endTime": 211.35199999999998,
    "text": "How's everythig going today?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.352,
    "endTime": 212.71200000000002,
    "text": "Probably(?) great."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 532.2,
    "endTime": 534.589,
    "text": "Probably great? Are you having a good week?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 534.589,
    "endTime": 535.7600000000001,
    "text": "Yes I do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 535.76,
    "endTime": 544.17,
    "text": "9 out of 12 people didn't answer the question \"How are you?\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 544.17,
    "endTime": 554.03,
    "text": "but responded \"Hey Jun.\" or \"Hey, how are you?\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 554.03,
    "endTime": 560.769,
    "text": "In other words, we have found that \"How are you?\" is"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 560.769,
    "endTime": 569.03,
    "text": "used as a greeting like \"Hi / Hello.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 569.03,
    "endTime": 571.579,
    "text": "Apart from that, there were three people who responded \"I'm good.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 571.579,
    "endTime": 579.1999999999999,
    "text": "and one person each for \"Excellent.\" \"Super.\" \"Alright.\" \"Fine.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 579.2,
    "endTime": 582.2900000000001,
    "text": "I only asked 12 Americans who live in L.A. in this video,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 582.29,
    "endTime": 587.05,
    "text": "so it's only a tiny sample,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 587.05,
    "endTime": 591.12,
    "text": "therefore I can't state anything conclusive here,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 591.12,
    "endTime": 599.839,
    "text": "but one thing we can say is, the question \"How are you?\" is"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 599.839,
    "endTime": 606.36,
    "text": "used as \"Hello\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 606.36,
    "endTime": 609.86,
    "text": "People who responded to the question \"How are you?\" in all kinds of ways"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 609.86,
    "endTime": 618.8100000000001,
    "text": "such as \"I'm good.\" \"I'm super.\" \"Excellent.\" \"I'm doing alright.\" \"I'm fine.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 618.81,
    "endTime": 624.27,
    "text": "so there is no one right respond to the question."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 624.27,
    "endTime": 630.18,
    "text": "The safest way to respond to the quesion would be \"I'm good.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 630.18,
    "endTime": 634.9899999999999,
    "text": "but it also depends on your preference,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 634.99,
    "endTime": 647.1,
    "text": "so pick one that you feel most comfortable saying."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 647.1,
    "endTime": 646.1800000000001,
    "text": "Lastly, I would like to add one more thing. When you want to ask back how they are doing,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 646.18,
    "endTime": 652.3389999999999,
    "text": "don't use \"And you?\" but use someting like \"How are you?\" or \"How about you?\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 652.339,
    "endTime": 660.149,
    "text": "They sound more natural."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 660.149,
    "endTime": 664.589,
    "text": "I have written about what Americans use besides \"How are you?\" and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 664.589,
    "endTime": 673.11,
    "text": "how they respond when they greet each other on my blog, so click the link below for details."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 673.11,
    "endTime": 675.0600000000001,
    "text": "How was today's lesson?"
  },
  {
